title: Dancing.with.the.Stars.AU.s14e03.Missing.Dance.PDTV.x264.Hector.
description:
Folks, I am so sorry that cap of episode 3 was incomplete. 
I am trying really hard to upload as many Australian shows as I can for people.
This is the part that is missing.
It follows on from the 32 minutes and 34 second mark of my original file.
I am also aware that this is very sloppy and that I should be reuploading a REPACK.
But, that would mean most people would have to download 1Gb just to see the 100mb part they missed.
Not only that, I am not convinced that a REPACK would get enough seeds to share around.
Sometimes you gotta make a judgement call and it won't please everyone lol!
